Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.94,0:01:27.02,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,僅有空虛又怎夠將我填飽？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.02,0:01:28.15,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Morning morning
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.74,0:01:35.12,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,立足原點  保持新鮮
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.12,0:01:38.29,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做我所願
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.29,0:01:41.08,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Every night, every time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.08,0:01:48.00,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,活至盡興  玩到疲倦
